00:15:42,240 --> 00:15:44,159
that the ingredients are fresh every day.

285
00:15:44,159 --> 00:15:45,320
What are you looking for today?

286
00:15:45,320 --> 00:15:47,600
- This is yellow.
- This one's good.

287
00:15:47,600 --> 00:15:49,559
This one has turned pink.

288
00:15:49,559 --> 00:15:50,879
What color is the cuttlefish?

289
00:15:50,879 --> 00:15:52,519
It's black, just look.

290
00:15:52,519 --> 00:15:55,399
Please deliver these things to my shop.

291
00:15:57,600 --> 00:16:00,759
Only after these things are done,
can Mr. Qiang rest.

292
00:16:00,759 --> 00:16:03,440
And by evening, he has to start preparing again

293
00:16:03,440 --> 00:16:05,720
for another busy day.

294
00:16:05,720 --> 00:16:07,080
Remember to deliver on time, okay?

295
00:16:07,080 --> 00:16:09,864
Alright, alright.

296
00:16:15,399 --> 00:16:17,919
It's not that I'm afraid of messing up.

297
00:16:19,240 --> 00:16:21,759
I don't know

298
00:16:21,759 --> 00:16:25,279
if I can be as dedicated

299
00:16:26,480 --> 00:16:29,288
and as good as them.

300
00:16:36,360 --> 00:16:37,440
Do you remember my first day

301
00:16:37,440 --> 00:16:39,360
in Macau?

302
00:16:39,360 --> 00:16:40,960
My phone was broken.

303
00:16:40,960 --> 00:16:44,240
I went to the shop for repairs,
and the boss said it can't be rushed.

304
00:16:44,240 --> 00:16:47,039
It was because of you
that I got it that very night.

305
00:16:47,039 --> 00:16:49,120
I'll treat you to a meal another day,
something delicious.

306
00:16:49,120 --> 00:16:50,440
- Lobster over rice.
- Got it.

307
00:16:50,440 --> 00:16:52,799
And the restaurant we ate at on the first day.

308
00:16:52,799 --> 00:16:54,759
At that time, I thought I had found

309
00:16:54,759 --> 00:16:56,559
a very niche restaurant.

310
00:16:56,559 --> 00:16:58,440
But as soon as I walked in, I found out that

311
00:16:58,440 --> 00:17:01,240
the clerk was your neighbor.

312
00:17:01,240 --> 00:17:04,480
It seems like wherever you go,
there are a lot of people you know.

313
00:17:04,480 --> 00:17:06,039
- Please deliver it to Zhen Qiang for me later.
- Alright, sure.

314
00:17:06,039 --> 00:17:08,160
I brought a birthday gift for Bin.

315
00:17:08,160 --> 00:17:09,880
Hey, is there anyone

316
00:17:09,880 --> 00:17:12,440
that you don't know in Macau?

317
00:17:14,359 --> 00:17:17,279
Macau is a small place.

318
00:17:17,279 --> 00:17:19,359
As long as you stay long enough,

319
00:17:19,359 --> 00:17:22,160
you'll know someone everywhere you go.

320
00:17:22,160 --> 00:17:23,880
No, it's not like that.

321
00:17:23,880 --> 00:17:26,039
It's because of you.

322
00:17:28,559 --> 00:17:30,880
I've been striving alone for so many years.

323
00:17:30,880 --> 00:17:34,680
I've only interacted with the neighbors
in the chat group.

324
00:17:34,680 --> 00:17:38,480
But you remember
the birthday of your neighbor's child.

325
00:17:43,279 --> 00:17:46,119
Perhaps even you haven't realized.

326
00:17:46,119 --> 00:17:48,440
You have a certain

327
00:17:49,039 --> 00:17:51,440
unique charm

328
00:17:52,200 --> 00:17:54,440
that makes people feel

329
00:17:54,440 --> 00:17:57,839
trust and reliance.

330
00:17:59,680 --> 00:18:02,000
Mr. Xu is just like you.

331
00:18:02,000 --> 00:18:03,640
People around you,

332
00:18:03,640 --> 00:18:05,119
the things that happen to them,

333
00:18:05,119 --> 00:18:06,920
the difficulties they encounter,

334
00:18:06,920 --> 00:18:08,559
you all deal with it

335
00:18:08,559 --> 00:18:12,160
as if it were your own matters.

336
00:18:12,160 --> 00:18:14,799
You don't know that people like you

337
00:18:14,799 --> 00:18:17,599
are actually very precious.

338
00:18:22,079 --> 00:18:24,519
I'm not as good as you say.

339
00:18:26,792 --> 00:18:31,039
<i>♫ Everything seems all too ordinary ♫</i>

340
00:18:31,039 --> 00:18:33,440
Mr. Xu once told me

341
00:18:33,440 --> 00:18:34,799
that the reason he opened Zhen Qiang

342
00:18:34,799 --> 00:18:37,160
was because

343
00:18:37,160 --> 00:18:39,680
what he wanted

344
00:18:39,680 --> 00:18:42,160
was his neighbors

345
00:18:42,160 --> 00:18:46,480
and his friends together.

346
00:18:47,359 --> 00:18:49,519
Everyone is brought together

347
00:18:49,519 --> 00:18:51,680
by fate.

348
00:18:52,279 --> 00:18:55,279
This is the purpose of Zhen Qiang's existence.

349
00:18:57,839 --> 00:18:59,759
I also remember Mr. Xu saying

350
00:18:59,759 --> 00:19:02,160
that even if one day,

351
00:19:02,160 --> 00:19:05,519
Zhen Qiang really can't continue.

352
00:19:05,519 --> 00:19:08,119
It's alright.

353
00:19:08,119 --> 00:19:10,519
That would mean the fate has run its course.

354
00:19:12,448 --> 00:19:14,848
<i>♫ But, baby ♫</i>

355
00:19:14,848 --> 00:19:18,208
<i>♫ Life is more than this ♫</i>

356
00:19:18,208 --> 00:19:20,608
<i>♫ We are in this world ♫</i>

357
00:19:20,608 --> 00:19:23,000
<i>♫ To feel the sunshine ♫</i>

358
00:19:23,000 --> 00:19:25,119
So I really think that you

359
00:19:25,119 --> 00:19:28,000
shouldn't put too much pressure on yourself.

360
00:19:29,359 --> 00:19:31,960
You should just follow

361
00:19:31,960 --> 00:19:34,240
the life creed that you and Mr. Xu believe in

362
00:19:34,240 --> 00:19:36,400
and live that way.

363
00:19:37,160 --> 00:19:40,279
Just try your best to do well

364
00:19:40,279 --> 00:19:42,680
the things that are in front of you.

365
00:19:43,440 --> 00:19:45,000
Live one day at a time.

366
00:19:45,000 --> 00:19:47,079
Each day you have is a day.

367
00:19:47,839 --> 00:19:49,880
Do it the way you want to.

368
00:19:49,880 --> 00:19:52,160
And I don't think that doing it your way
would be anything less than good.

369
00:19:52,160 --> 00:19:57,408
<i>♫ Feel free to have a beautiful dream ♫</i>

370
00:19:57,408 --> 00:20:02,912
<i>♫ You've always had wings ♫</i>

371
00:20:02,912 --> 00:20:10,912
<i>♫ Little fish also have their own ocean ♫</i>

372
00:20:20,400 --> 00:20:22,839
I thought of a joke.

373
00:20:23,960 --> 00:20:27,519
A calf, a lamb, a piglet.

374
00:20:27,519 --> 00:20:28,640
The three of them

375
00:20:28,640 --> 00:20:31,480
walk into Zhen Qiang at the same time.

376
00:20:34,480 --> 00:20:38,279
Who won't get beaten up?

377
00:20:40,960 --> 00:20:43,720
That's a tough joke.

378
00:20:45,559 --> 00:20:47,119
The piglet, right?

379
00:20:47,119 --> 00:20:48,799
No.

380
00:20:48,799 --> 00:20:50,880
Then who is it?

381
00:20:52,480 --> 00:20:55,272
The lamb.

382
00:20:55,880 --> 00:20:58,880
Because Zhen Qiang

383
00:20:58,880 --> 00:21:00,960
never closes.

384
00:21:00,960 --> 00:21:05,440
<i>♫ No growth can be stopped ♫</i>

385
00:21:05,440 --> 00:21:08,640
<i>♫ Though the future is uncertain ♫</i>

386
00:21:08,640 --> 00:21:10,912
<i>♫ The answers lie on the road ahead ♫</i>

387
00:21:10,912 --> 00:21:13,344
<i>♫ Love what you love ♫</i>

388
00:21:13,344 --> 00:21:17,184
<i>♫ Go and accomplish what your heart desires ♫</i>

389
00:21:17,184 --> 00:21:19,584
<i>♫ Tears also sparkle ♫</i>

390
00:21:19,584 --> 00:21:23,488
<i>♫ Not frustrated for anyone ♫</i>

391
00:21:23,488 --> 00:21:25,856
<i>♫ Look up at the sky ♫</i>

392
00:21:25,856 --> 00:21:30,592
<i>♫ Forgive all the sorrows and mistakes ♫</i>

393
00:21:30,592 --> 00:21:36,480
<i>♫ No longer afraid to go far ♫</i>

394
00:21:36,480 --> 00:21:44,480
<i>♫ Little fish also have their own ocean ♫</i>

395
00:21:50,920 --> 00:21:52,400
Mr. Xu and Casey are already in the elevator.

396
00:21:52,400 --> 00:21:54,440
They'll be here soon.

397
00:21:55,240 --> 00:21:57,559
- Mr. Xu.
- Director Tong.

398
00:21:57,559 --> 00:21:59,720
- Hello.
- Hello, thank you for taking the time

399
00:21:59,720 --> 00:22:00,880
to come to our meeting.

400
00:22:00,880 --> 00:22:03,039
- Please sit.
- Please.

401
00:22:03,559 --> 00:22:05,359
Firstly, I must extend to you

402
00:22:05,359 --> 00:22:07,640
our most sincere apologies
on behalf of our company.

403
00:22:07,640 --> 00:22:09,759
Our team will definitely cooperate fully

404
00:22:09,759 --> 00:22:12,079
to ensure the issue is resolved properly.

405
00:22:12,079 --> 00:22:13,119
To my knowledge,

406
00:22:13,119 --> 00:22:14,559
before your new member

407
00:22:14,559 --> 00:22:15,880
Amy came,

408
00:22:15,880 --> 00:22:18,400
the shooting had always been orderly.

409
00:22:18,400 --> 00:22:21,880
So let's see how this can be resolved.

410
00:22:22,720 --> 00:22:24,240
Actually, from the beginning of this project,

411
00:22:24,240 --> 00:22:26,319
it was Miss Mai who was coordinating with me.

412
00:22:26,319 --> 00:22:28,519
She is very familiar
with the content of the plan

413
00:22:28,519 --> 00:22:29,640
and she has done a lot of preparatory work

414
00:22:29,640 --> 00:22:30,759
for the shooting in Macau.

415
00:22:30,759 --> 00:22:32,319
So we still think

416
00:22:32,319 --> 00:22:33,640
it's more reliable

417
00:22:33,640 --> 00:22:35,880
for her to be in charge.

418
00:22:39,880 --> 00:22:40,880
I see.

419
00:22:40,880 --> 00:22:43,440
Today, I am here to make a promise to you

420
00:22:43,440 --> 00:22:44,519
that a similar situation

421
00:22:44,519 --> 00:22:47,000
will absolutely not occur again.

422
00:22:47,000 --> 00:22:48,359
Xinghao has always been our

423
00:22:48,359 --> 00:22:49,880
highly valued client.

424
00:22:49,880 --> 00:22:53,000
We will definitely not fail
the trust you have placed in us.

425
00:22:53,000 --> 00:22:55,880
The project will continue to be managed by Mai.

426
00:22:55,880 --> 00:22:58,079
Amy will not be involved.

427
00:23:00,064 --> 00:23:01,480
Okay.

428
00:23:01,480 --> 00:23:04,440
Mai, there are no issues
with the progress, right?

429
00:23:04,440 --> 00:23:06,079
Yes, we have actually adjusted the plan,

430
00:23:06,079 --> 00:23:07,240
so the progress of the entire major plan

431
00:23:07,240 --> 00:23:09,400
will not be affected at all.

432
00:23:09,400 --> 00:23:10,759
Very good.

433
00:23:10,759 --> 00:23:14,240
Then, let's leave it at that.

434
00:23:14,240 --> 00:23:15,880
- Okay.
- Okay?

435
00:23:15,880 --> 00:23:18,640
Thank you, Mr. Xu, for trusting us.

436
00:23:18,640 --> 00:23:20,079
- Take care, Director Tong
- Thank you.

437
00:23:20,079 --> 00:23:22,079
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

438
00:23:29,680 --> 00:23:31,000
By the way, Casey,

439
00:23:31,000 --> 00:23:32,440
the headquarters

440
00:23:32,440 --> 00:23:33,920
has assigned a task to me.

441
00:23:33,920 --> 00:23:35,319
- I'd like you to help me take a look.
- Okay.

442
00:23:35,319 --> 00:23:37,319
They want to hold a charity auction gala

443
00:23:37,319 --> 00:23:39,559
to enhance our brand image.

444
00:23:39,559 --> 00:23:41,039
There's a philanthropist
from the mainland called

445
00:23:41,039 --> 00:23:42,079
Chloe Liu.

446
00:23:42,079 --> 00:23:43,160
She wants to organize

447
00:23:43,160 --> 00:23:44,240
a painting exhibition focusing
on children with autism

448
00:23:44,240 --> 00:23:45,279
to raise awareness and care.

449
00:23:45,279 --> 00:23:47,640
I think that's a very good entry point.

450
00:23:47,640 --> 00:23:49,240
I will send you
the information about Chloe Liu.

451
00:23:49,240 --> 00:23:50,960
See if you can get in touch
with her in advance.

452
00:23:50,960 --> 00:23:53,519
I'll check if she has any events
to attend in Macau recently.

453
00:23:53,519 --> 00:23:54,759
I'll go see her,

454
00:23:54,759 --> 00:23:56,799
get to know her, and then
see how to arrange it.

455
00:23:56,799 --> 00:23:59,880
Very good.

456
00:23:59,880 --> 00:24:01,200
Actually, you could go take a look

457
00:24:01,200 --> 00:24:02,920
at how other galleries conduct their auctions.

458
00:24:02,920 --> 00:24:03,960
Not necessarily in Macau.

459
00:24:03,960 --> 00:24:05,359
Just to have a reference style.

460
00:24:05,359 --> 00:24:07,759
Alright, I'll immediately
look up different teams.

461
00:24:07,759 --> 00:24:10,152
Okay.

462
00:24:11,759 --> 00:24:14,728
I'll go to work first.

463
00:24:25,720 --> 00:24:26,759
What are you doing here?

464
00:24:26,759 --> 00:24:28,000
Don't you have to go to the site?

465
00:24:28,000 --> 00:24:29,480
Yes, I do.

466
00:24:29,480 --> 00:24:32,759
But before I go, I wanted
to talk with you for a moment.

467
00:24:33,839 --> 00:24:36,616
Okay.

468
00:24:38,359 --> 00:24:40,000
The shopping mall downstairs is so big.

469
00:24:40,000 --> 00:24:43,480
But the offices upstairs are so crowded.

470
00:24:43,480 --> 00:24:45,440
Did you come up here
just to talk about these things?

471
00:24:45,440 --> 00:24:47,359
I want to buy something for a friend.
Is there a discount?

472
00:24:47,359 --> 00:24:49,640
If you have nothing else to say, I'll leave.

473
00:24:51,960 --> 00:24:53,240
You know, Dad

474
00:24:53,240 --> 00:24:54,599
is really very stubborn.

475
00:24:54,599 --> 00:24:56,880
He has his own way of doing things.

476
00:24:56,880 --> 00:24:59,240
He's old-fashioned and won't take advice.

477
00:24:59,240 --> 00:25:01,599
He always misunderstands others' intentions.

478
00:25:01,599 --> 00:25:04,680
His words can be unpleasant, and he
doesn't apologize when he hurts someone.

479
00:25:04,680 --> 00:25:06,359
From childhood to adulthood,

480
00:25:06,359 --> 00:25:10,440
he neglected you just to focus on Zhen Qiang.

481
00:25:10,440 --> 00:25:12,480
I know you must feel
uncomfortable and aggrieved inside.

482
00:25:12,480 --> 00:25:14,240
I understand what you're saying, okay.

483
00:25:14,240 --> 00:25:15,400
Wait a minute, I haven't finished.

484
00:25:15,400 --> 00:25:17,880
Can you let me finish first?

485
00:25:18,480 --> 00:25:20,720
Okay, go ahead.

486
00:25:21,319 --> 00:25:22,319
I'm not qualified to say this,

487
00:25:22,319 --> 00:25:24,720
but I know it's very unfair.

488
00:25:24,720 --> 00:25:26,359
But no matter what,

489
00:25:26,359 --> 00:25:29,599
you're my elder brother,
the eldest son of the Xu family.

490
00:25:29,599 --> 00:25:32,720
Every one of us cares about you a lot.

491
00:25:36,599 --> 00:25:38,880
I believe they would all be proud of you

492
00:25:38,880 --> 00:25:41,000
for your achievements today.

493
00:25:41,000 --> 00:25:43,240
Dad is getting old.

494
00:25:43,240 --> 00:25:45,759
It's hard for him to change his personality.

495
00:25:46,839 --> 00:25:49,440
So as his sons,

496
00:25:49,440 --> 00:25:51,880
all we can do is be tolerant.

497
00:25:51,880 --> 00:25:52,960
So I hope you won't

498
00:25:52,960 --> 00:25:54,160
hold so much against him, okay?

499
00:25:54,160 --> 00:25:56,720
I'm not holding so much against him.
I'm not in a position to do that.

500
00:25:56,720 --> 00:25:58,720
I'm not you.

501
00:26:09,960 --> 00:26:12,960
I'm not forcing you to apologize to him.

502
00:26:12,960 --> 00:26:14,720
I just hope that you

503
00:26:14,720 --> 00:26:16,799
can speak all your thoughts

504
00:26:16,799 --> 00:26:18,960
out loud for him to hear.

505
00:26:21,759 --> 00:26:25,519
Only then does this emotional knot
have a chance to be untied.

506
00:26:25,519 --> 00:26:28,200
Okay?

507
00:26:35,440 --> 00:26:38,120
Alright, it's all good now.

508
00:26:38,640 --> 00:26:40,839
You promised me.

509
00:26:41,880 --> 00:26:43,039
Thank you, Mr. Xu.

510
00:26:43,039 --> 00:26:44,480
Crazy.

511
00:26:44,480 --> 00:26:46,319
Seriously, I want to buy
something for a friend.

512
00:26:46,319 --> 00:26:48,880
- Do you have any discounted items?
- No.

513
00:26:56,448 --> 00:27:00,040
<i>[Zhen Qiang]</i>

514
00:27:16,599 --> 00:27:17,640
Mr. Wei,

515
00:27:17,640 --> 00:27:19,640
- Where's my dad?
- Hao, you're here.

516
00:27:26,359 --> 00:27:28,640
Dad.

517
00:27:28,640 --> 00:27:31,336
Sit down.

518
00:27:41,400 --> 00:27:43,440
Do you need anything?

519
00:27:44,279 --> 00:27:45,880
No.

520
00:27:45,880 --> 00:27:47,440
I haven't been back in a long time.

521
00:27:47,440 --> 00:27:49,680
So I came to take a look.

522
00:28:00,200 --> 00:28:01,680
If you still want

523
00:28:01,680 --> 00:28:04,160
to persuade me to sell the shop,

524
00:28:04,759 --> 00:28:07,176
no need to say anything.

525
00:28:18,440 --> 00:28:19,880
In your heart,

526
00:28:19,880 --> 00:28:22,720
is this shop really that important to you, Dad?

527
00:28:25,279 --> 00:28:26,920
After all these years,

528
00:28:26,920 --> 00:28:28,720
I feel that this home,

529
00:28:28,720 --> 00:28:31,759
this shop is the eldest brother,

530
00:28:31,759 --> 00:28:33,960
followed by Le and Bao.

531
00:28:33,960 --> 00:28:36,200
And I am just an outsider.

532
00:28:37,319 --> 00:28:39,680
Whether I am here or not

533
00:28:39,680 --> 00:28:42,472
is not very important.

534
00:28:44,160 --> 00:28:45,799
I understand

535
00:28:45,799 --> 00:28:46,880
that when you started Zhen Qiang,

536
00:28:46,880 --> 00:28:48,720
it was very difficult.

537
00:28:48,720 --> 00:28:50,960
You were too busy to take care of me,
so you sent me to Grandpa's.

538
00:28:50,960 --> 00:28:52,160
I have never blamed you, Dad.

539
00:28:52,160 --> 00:28:54,480
I really haven't.

540
00:28:54,480 --> 00:28:56,480
But I sometimes reminisce,

541
00:28:56,480 --> 00:28:57,480
once the shop was on track,

542
00:28:57,480 --> 00:29:00,559
when we had almost made enough money,

543
00:29:00,559 --> 00:29:01,680
could you have spared some time

544
00:29:01,680 --> 00:29:03,799
to spend with us?

545
00:29:12,720 --> 00:29:15,960
Do you know that I have
to support not only you,

546
00:29:15,960 --> 00:29:18,839
but also this group of old buddies?

547
00:29:20,359 --> 00:29:23,519
Their whole families depend on Zhen Qiang
for a living, do you know that?

548
00:29:23,519 --> 00:29:24,920
I know, Dad.

549
00:29:24,920 --> 00:29:26,119
So many big bosses

